{"tid":2451369,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「蒼天已死，黃天當立」？北京重度空氣污染 沙塵暴天空出現罕見「藍太陽」 網說嚇傻","createTime":"2021-03-18T05:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T09:23:23.000Z","uid":373900,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"01d24d9d1a61dababc5e9995f2f4e3c410fc12ff","tid":2451369,"uid":373900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQFdx9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQFdx9C.png&h=474b9f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRDR4iQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRDR4iQ.jpg&h=fdc203b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9EqpiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9EqpiQ.jpg&h=1821c66f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國北京市15日氣候、天象都不平靜，除颳起近10年最強沙塵暴外，不少民眾更因此在視野相對良好處，捕捉到清晰的&ldquo;藍太陽&rdquo;奇景，就好像在火星上看太陽一樣，在網絡平台上引發熱烈討論，有人擔憂&ldquo;天有異象，大事發生&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據東森新聞今天報道稱，北京天空驚見&ldquo;藍太陽&rdquo;...陸網憂：出大事了！消息說，2021年3月15日，北京市視野相對清晰處，擡頭可見藍太陽景觀。<br />\n<br />\n據《北京日報》引述大陸國家天文台研究員苟利軍說明，&ldquo;藍太陽&rdquo;也與沙塵暴有關，因為今日（3月15日）北京大氣中的塵埃顆粒發生了米氏散射，而非熟悉的瑞利散射；所謂米氏散射，系因沙塵粒徑通常大於可見光波長，波長最接近粒徑的紅橙光散射明顯，逆光回望太陽時紅光較少而略呈藍色。<br />\n<br />\n該報道綜合陸媒消息和大陸網友在網絡上分享的&ldquo;藍太陽&rdquo;畫面，明顯可見太陽周邊呈現藍色光芒，網友們紛紛感嘆&ldquo;好美&rdquo;，但也有人擔憂&ldquo;天有異象，大事發生&rdquo;，或呼籲&ldquo;要好好保護地球。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n據該報道說，受沙塵暴影響，北京市大部分地區今日普遍能見度不佳，無法看到完整的藍太陽景觀。<br />\n<br />\n據聯合新聞網說，北京天空竟然出現藍色太陽！近期大陸天候相當不平靜，除了颳起了10幾年來最強的沙塵暴造成6人死亡，80餘人失蹤以外，現在北京的天空又出現了藍太陽，瞬間引起眾多網友熱烈討論，不少人紛紛擔心&ldquo;天有異象，有大事發生&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今（15）日北京出現了沙塵天氣，就有眼尖的網友發現天空的太陽周圍呈現了藍色的光芒，就如同在火星看到的一樣，不少人連忙拍下來上傳到社群網站上，有些網友紛紛驚呼這也太神奇了，但也有網友憂心忡忡地認為天有異象，恐怕會有大事發生，也有不少網友開玩笑地說，&ldquo;證明火星上可以生存&rdquo;、&ldquo;這明明是我屋內的大燈&rdquo;、&ldquo;啊？火星校區已經開始招生了嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n北京遭遇近10年來最強沙塵暴吹襲。受冷空氣和蒙古氣旋影響，內地北方12省市出現沙塵暴，包括新疆、內蒙古、甘肅、寧夏、陝西、山西、河北、北京、天津、黑龍江、吉林、遼寧。從凌晨開始，漫天黃沙掩至，以致北京清晨時分的天空比傍晚還要昏暗。北京市內能見度只有數百米，故宮、天安門城樓、國家大劇院、鳥巢及中央電視台大樓等地標建築，均隱藏在滿天黃沙後，使人難窺全貌。<br />\n<br />\n北京氣象部門從凌晨開始，先後發布沙塵暴藍色、黃色預警，呼籲市民暫停露天集會和戶外活動。北京生態環境監測中心清晨7時發布信息顯示，北京污染級別為6級，空氣質量達嚴重污染，主要污染物為PM10。至上午10時，北京城所有區縣的PM2.5與PM10均已達到6級嚴重污染程度。據北方地區遙感圖顯示，今次沙塵暴起源於<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><em><span class=\"red\">蒙古南部</span></em></strong></span>。預計未來兩日空氣質量將有所改善。<br />\n<br />\n北京市三環現況<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tucaofakenews/status/1372336831841202177?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftucaofakenews%2Fstatus%2F1372336831841202177%3Fs%3D21&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=7487d9d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftucaofakenews%2Fstatus%2F1372336831841202177%3Fs%3D21&h=d70e78ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tucaofakenews/status/1372336831841202177?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n近十多年，南蒙古中佔區受到對礦產等資源的過度開採，造成重度環境破壞及污染。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPmwjWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPmwjWU.jpg&h=0323d0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7HLpoA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7HLpoA.jpg&h=bc3d39fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CUm8naf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCUm8naf.jpg&h=ca252d37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pvt6TgW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvt6TgW.jpg&h=5829d748&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y71TygX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY71TygX.gif&h=3c4d94bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDqEtQh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDqEtQh.jpg&h=5a3cc054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgnvAus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgnvAus.png&h=08777095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南蒙曾經的「草原風吹草低見牛羊」，已一去不復返<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒需常在當地打「藍天保衛戰」<br />\n<a href=\"https://coal.in-en.com/html/coal-2555733.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcoal.in-en.com%2Fhtml%2Fcoal-2555733.shtml&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=1592bb88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://coal.in-en.com/html/coal-2555733.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n南蒙古草原消失實況，2012年<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/kalaok/6955970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Fkalaok%2F6955970&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=7c514d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/kalaok/6955970</a>"},{"pid":"6b6df9a64dd38f13da602e970e8755d171526bb7","tid":2451369,"uid":7369,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"歐美班傻鳩仲覺得支那會減排<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d8525d830a9fa15a4e7549f74367b101f96ad4","tid":2451369,"uid":155815,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"紅太陽=毛主席<br />\n藍太陽=? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad612d0000e6acba4ab4d70b46684ab842df546","tid":2451369,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028fc1d357f416a5acc19722959361b2b06256bd","tid":2451369,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70d8525d830a9fa15a4e7549f74367b101f96ad4","tid":2451369,"uid":155815,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"紅太陽=毛主席<br />\n藍太陽=? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:12:03.000Z